I been to so many aquarium. Like estimate 11 to 13 around. So far i see Rainbow Aquarium which is at 78 Sungei Tengah Rd, Singapore 699003. Their items almost 90% or 95% product cheaper than majority outside. Photos reference for people to see. Plus they got 10% off discount on every items. Their price list before 10%.

But their fish not so clean and healthy compare to some aquarium outside. Share around and help the community. Good for those who first time and wants to save Budget $$.

text.text:
This wholesaler and fish farm specializes in aquarium supplies and aquatic pets - mostly tropical fishes and some varieties of shrimps. You can get everything you need to start an aquarium at home from nano tanks to huge ones as the sizes of fishes varies from nano to large ones. Prices are reasonable too and there are premium priced fishes as well. The viewing experience is great.
Recommended to drive here as it is quite far from the main road but still possible if needed. It is about 10-15mins walk from main road and nearest to the Choa Chu Kang estate.
